    "lines": [
      {"speaker": "小黄", "chinese": "我发现你花钱很节省。", "pinyin": "Wǒ fāxiàn nǐ huāqián hěn jiéshěng.", "english": "I notice you spend money frugally."},
      {"speaker": "小马", "chinese": "对,我从来不买奢侈品,能省就省。", "pinyin": "Duì, wǒ cónglái búmăi shēchǐpǐn, néng shěng jiù shěng.", "english": "Yes, I never buy luxury goods, save what I can."},
      {"speaker": "小黄", "chinese": "我喜欢让自己过得舒服一点儿,干吗跟自己过不去呢?", "pinyin": "Wǒ xǐhuān ràng zìjǐ guòde shūfu yìdiǎn'er, gānma gēn zìjǐ guòbuqù ne?", "english": "I like to live comfortably, why be hard on myself?"},
      {"speaker": "小马", "chinese": "你应该先订个计划,每月存多少,花多少,然后按照计划用钱。", "pinyin": "Nǐ yīnggāi xiān dìng ge jìhuà, měi yuè cún duōshao, huā duōshao, ránhòu ànzhào jìhuà yòngqián.", "english": "You should make a plan, decide how much to save and spend monthly, then stick to it."},
      {"speaker": "小黄", "chinese": "我的开销总是很大,老觉得钱不够用。", "pinyin": "Wǒ de kaixião zǒngshi hěn dà, lǎo juéde qián búgòu yòng.", "english": "My expenses are always large, I always feel short of money."},
      {"speaker": "小马", "chinese": "你可以每天记账,然后检查一下,减少不必要的开支。", "pinyin": "Nǐ kěyǐ měi tiān jì zhàng, ránhòu jiǎnchá yìxia, jiǎnshao búbìyào de kāizhī.", "english": "You can keep accounts daily, then check and reduce unnecessary expenses."}
    ]
  },
